      • process

        public void process(TickEvent event)
        TickEvent handler. Checks if simulation is in sync with tick events. It means currentIteration must be one less than number received in the event. Any exception caught during execution of this handler causes termination of simulation.
        Overrides:
        process in class AbstractEventHandler

      • process

        public void process(WaitingPassengersEvent event)
        WaitingPassengersEvent handler. Takes list containing information on waiting passengers and calls BusManager.processWaitingPassengersQueryResponse(java.util.Map) Any exception caught during execution of this handler causes termination of simulation.
        Overrides:
        process in class AbstractEventHandler

      • process

        public void process(BusDeparturesEvent event)
        BusDeparturesEvent handler. Takes list containing infomarion on bus departures delivered in the event and calls BusManager.processBusDeparturesList(java.util.List). After that sends bus mockups BusMockupsEvent reflecting current state of the fleet and, subsequently, sends ModuleReadyEvent. Any exception caught during execution of this handler causes termination of simulation.
        Overrides:
        process in class AbstractEventHandler

      • process

        public void process(ChangeReleasingFrequencyEvent event)
        ChangeReleasingFrequencyEvent handler. Calls Terminus.changeReleasingFrequency(long) with argument Retrieved from the event.
